what type of autmation you have done in k8

Ans.
In Kubernetes, I’ve automated CI/CD deployments using Helm and GitOps, autoscaling with HPA/VPA, 
infrastructure provisioning via Terraform, monitoring/alerts with Prometheus and Grafana, 
secrets/config updates through ConfigMaps and Vault, and DR/backups. 
I also automated routine cluster maintenance to improve reliability and reduce manual effort.”

